      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or age. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a smooth engine, crisp transmission, and every single feature functioning exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment.",
